original_title: UFO: The Greatest Story Ever Denied III - UFOs from Outer Space
overview: There is no telling what is really going on deep in space. But one thing is absolutely for certain, there is not one film or photo in this movie that was taken from earth. You will see real life UFOs captured in the far regions of space by NASA and foreign space agencies.
title: UFO: The Greatest Story Ever Denied III - UFOs from Outer Space
